	<GU_Enable_RnR>Enable Ride and Roll module</GU_Enable_RnR>
	<GU_Enable_RnR_Description>Disabling this module will remove functionality related to pawns using mounts to get around the map out of convenience or for jobs. Changing this setting requires a restart.</GU_Enable_RnR_Description>
	
	<GU_Enable_BattleMounts>Enable Battle Mounts module</GU_Enable_BattleMounts>
	<GU_Enable_BattleMounts_Description>Disabling this module will remove functionality related to pawns (both colonists and enemies) using animals as battle mounts. Changing this setting requires a restart.</GU_Enable_BattleMounts_Description>
	
	<GU_Enable_Caravans>Enable Caravans module</GU_Enable_Caravans>
	<GU_Enable_Caravans_Description>Disabling this module will remove functionality related to pawns (both colonists and friendlies) riding animals when they exit and enter the map. Changing this setting requires a restart.</GU_Enable_Caravans_Description>
	
	<GU_Enable_Mechanoids>Enable Mechanoids module</GU_Enable_Mechanoids>
	<GU_Enable_Mechanoids_Description>Disabling this module will remove functionality related to pawns (both colonists and enemies) using mechanoids as mounts. Changing this setting requires a restart.</GU_Enable_Mechanoids_Description>

	<GU_Enable_SaddleUp>Enable Saddle Up module</GU_Enable_SaddleUp>
	<GU_Enable_SaddleUp_Description>Disabling this module will remove the gizmo to go and mount a nearby animal or mech.</GU_Enable_SaddleUp_Description>
	
	<GU_Enable_Ideology>Enable Ideology module</GU_Enable_Ideology>
	<GU_Enable_Ideology_Description>Disabling this module will remove functionality related to Ideology DLC. Changing this setting requires a restart.</GU_Enable_Ideology_Description>

